的現象，試論此波新冠疫情（covid-19）所產生的媒介恐慌現象，在傳播
效果上有那些本質上與現象上的差異？（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:33:19+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c2b45d71426e", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110090", "c": "318", "s": "0514", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "傳播理論", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "heelevel3", "civil_category": "新聞(選試英文)"}'::jsonb, NULL),
